name: ObjectGraphIterator_nextTest
description: Unit tests for the next() method of the ObjectGraphIterator class.

test_cases.name: testNext_Success
test_cases.description: Tests the successful iteration over elements using the next() method.

test_cases.name: testNext_NoSuchElementException
test_cases.description: Tests that NoSuchElementException is thrown when calling next() on an exhausted iterator.

test_cases.name: testNext_WithTransformer
test_cases.description: Tests the next() method when a transformer is used to transform elements.

test_cases.name: testNext_EmptyIterator
test_cases.description: Tests that NoSuchElementException is thrown when calling next() on an empty iterator.
